Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the kind of attitude you should have towards your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think your attitude is a little arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've suffered a lot up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...Otani's neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend sure is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you were being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Mimi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.05,Title,,0,0,0,,Declaration of War!!\NThe Dangerous Beauty Who Burns With Jealousy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?! Why didn't you tell us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say when you asked her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's great. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Is this true, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahdsakafajdags!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the comedy duo is finally a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me why, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about this seriously! It's weird! Choosing a guy like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, a guy like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it, mini-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go getting cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's getting cocky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this day would come eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei was looking for you two earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget your summer homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at this stage there's nothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn it in by Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work on it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to the library with Suzuki and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm in a quiet place like the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be all "eek!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be all "eek," won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought your girlfriend over?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought today's milk for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,M-milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She brings me milk every day, saying it'll make me taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I've brought something really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is high-calcium milk,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...straight from the pastures of Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing else, hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. But I wanted to chat with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We're gonna study now, so you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Otani. It'll just be for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-chan, could you come here for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan, you're pretty tall and slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How tall are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,172 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Same as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But A-chan always said he'd never go out with a girl taller than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. That'd be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't seem to mind my height...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know that A-chan's last girlfriend was really short?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She was small and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I gave up on A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Otani, Mimi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But A-chan only likes short girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I bring him milk every day, so that he'll grow taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that when A-chan grew taller than me, I'd become his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... uh... Sorry, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sorry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of dirty trick did you pull to get him, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to thread a needle through your nostrils and tie a knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan can't possibly have a girlfriend like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Mimi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say my name in that disgusting voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get any closer to A-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll make what's left of your life extremely painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cake! Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the Mont Blanc cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend is really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a hallucination just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi, after you finish that, go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea she was a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's Otani-kun's neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying anything to Otani would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no point in worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go have some fun, now that we've turned in our homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's! Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens to me or what's said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as I have Otani's love, I'll be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend and I are really getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to hang out together today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. In that case, you two go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to walk home between two amazons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll look like a captured alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll smack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wa-Wait! Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it yet, hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to have a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally staring me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did someone like you come to be going out with A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I worked really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! I've been working really hard too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really cute when I'm with A-chan, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been acting like that ever since I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how tiring that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That would be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I give A-chan milk every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he hasn't grown at all since his first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I, on the other hand, was already over 170 cm when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already 168 cm when I was in the sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I've been put at the back because of my height since I was in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was even taller than the tallest boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Its a real pain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do, you always draw attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you talk, even just for a second, the teacher always sees—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why the hell am I reminiscing with an idiot like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You were trying to catch me off guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When A-chan was going out with that short, cute girl, I completely gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally. You'd think you had no chance with your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that deep down she would've been nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's not like you, Mimi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Deep down I'm really a nasty—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut that damn mouth of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you calling "nasty," you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So after he broke up with that great girlfriend, he moved on to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall and stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'm not going to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to win A-chan back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So-Sorry. Could you lend me some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have 50 yen on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,50...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some guts, walking into a family restaurant with only that much cash on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that I bought a magazine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked so cute and sweet that I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a special situation today, so I'll lend you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You sure are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I left my purse at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The total comes to 630 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is it that you like about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's nothing like your last girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taller than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she goes to family restaurants with only 50 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't see what's so great about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time or the place to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! I need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to. It's not like it's any of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you much more than she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I understand how Mimi-chan feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did A-chan say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he angry with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... I yelled at him and called him an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is an idiot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he say that in response to a confession? That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan is not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would be shocked by a sudden confession like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say bad things about A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never talked to him that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it and said something I shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, you cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault that my life is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do about it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat got your tongue? Why don't you try responding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lookin' for a fight, you dumb bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi...mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be really down, now that you've seen her true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that the Mimi I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...is fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she wants to act cute in front of the guy she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross, gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens because you say pointless things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Mimi-chan contacted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the three of us should do something after school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that her cover's blown, Mimi-chan's going to get serious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "serious"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen to an idiot like Otani if a pretty girl like her got serious about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let all of my efforts go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go wherever you want, A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, A-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just go away, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we play?\N What should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That one's free. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Mimi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan, come play with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to say to you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to reject me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,About Koizumi, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you liked Otani more than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that all  just talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his girlfriend. Like you'd know how it feels to be rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know how! I was rejected, too! Twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about giving up, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in the end I kept trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be his girlfriend now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he calls me an idiot, and says I'm gross all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly tell whether he actually likes me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you sayi—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love him more than I can say, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to give Otani up to someone who just runs away when she gets rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did Mimi-chan storm off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she can't deal with an idiot like you, so she's giving up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have hurt her a lot the first time you rejected her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But she worked hard to win you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is amazing, that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that you were saying back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about not being able to tell whether I actually like you or not, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, that was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You deliberately stood on higher steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't have been as cool if we were standing on level ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...but from now on, I hope we can be together like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you writing test questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking over what the students aim to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for them to make their final decisions, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like All Hanshin-Kyojin will finally have to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:45.04,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Career Guidance Questionnaire
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:45.04,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:45.04,Superscript,,0,0,0,,University
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do while you're away, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Premonition of Separation?! The Different Paths Risa and Otani Will Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.00,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Premonition of Separation?! The Different Paths Risa and Otani Will Walk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
